div.summary:
Lists draft quotas for each of the townships in Franklin county as
                    established by Lincoln's latest call for troops: Antrim, 79; Greencastle, 28;
                    Chambersburg, NW, 77; Chambersburg, SW, 73; Fannet, 20; Green, 70; Guilford, 75;
                    Hamilton, 28; Letterkenny, 52; Lurgan, 17; Metal, 12; Montgomery, 75;
                    Mercersburg, 19; Peters, 50; Quincy, 69; St. Thomas, 46; Southampton, 40;
                    Warren, 4; Washington, 56; Waynesboro, 25. Total draft quota for Franklin
                    county, 915.
